# 🚌 Bus Booking System (Golang + MySQL)

A simple REST API for bus ticket booking built with **Go (Golang)**, **MySQL**, and **Gorilla Mux**.  
Supports CRUD operations: Create, Read, Update, Delete bookings.

---

## ⚙️ Features
- Add new booking
- View all bookings
- Get booking by ID
- Update booking
- Delete booking

---

## 🚀 Tech Stack
- Go (net/http, Gorilla Mux)
- MySQL
- JSON-based REST API

---
